---
import InstructionNote from '../InstructionNote.astro';
---
<section id="strategy">
    <h2>Audience</h2>
    <h3>Inclusive Mission Statement</h3>
    <p>Splitli exists to make fitness education accessible for every body and every mind. Our mission is to deliver a clear and inclusive digital experience to those starting a fitness journey. Splitli prioritizes educating users of all abilities through inclusive design to build confidence, consistency, and strength. 
</p>

    <h3>Audience Considerations</h3>
    <h4>Users with Visual Impairments</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Semantic HTML structure</li>
        <li>Descriptive alt text for all images</li>
        <li>Skip-to-content navigation links</li>
        <li>Minimum 4.5:1 contrast ratio for normal text</li>
        <li>3:1 contrast for large text</li>
        <li>No reliance on color alone to convey meaning</li>
        <li>Text resizable up to 200% without breaking layout</li>
        <li>No auto-playing visual effects</li>
    </ul>

        <h4>Users with Cognitive & Learning Disabilities</h4>
        <ul>
        <li>Short paragraphs</li>
        <li>Plain language explanations</li>
        <li>Defined glossary terms</li>
        <li>Predictable navigation layout</li>
        <li>Limit clutter and unnecessary animations</li>
        <li>Clear CTA buttons</li>
        <li>No overwhelming dropdown menus</li>
        <li>Sans-serif fonts</li>
        <li>Minimum 16px body text</li>
        <li>Consistent page structure across all pages</li>
        <li>Progress indicators in interactive tools</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Users with Motor or Mobility Impairments</h4>
        <ul>
        <li>Full functionality without a mouse</li>
        <li>Logical tab order</li>
        <li>Visible focus indicators</li>
        <li>Buttons at least 44x44px</li>
        <li>Generous spacing between interactive elements</li>
        <li>Avoids tiny icons as primary actions</li>
        <li>No auto-advancing slides</li>
        </ul>
</section>